# Dodo Design System

## Theme

- **Dark mode only** — no light mode toggle
- Ratio: 70% dark, 20% yellow, 5% red, 5% white

## Brand Colors (CSS Variables)

```css
--dodo-yellow: #fee257;  /* Primary CTA, accents, highlights */
--dodo-red: #f01b24;     /* Destructive, promo badges, alerts */
--background: #0a0a0a;   /* Dark base */
--foreground: #ffffff;    /* Text */
```

## Tailwind Usage

```tsx
// CTA buttons
<Button className="bg-dodo-yellow text-black hover:bg-dodo-yellow/90">
// Promo badges
<Badge className="bg-dodo-red text-white">
// Cards
<div className="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg">
// Text
<p className="text-foreground">  // primary text
<p className="text-muted-foreground">  // secondary text
```

## Typography

| Role | Font | Usage |
|------|------|-------|
| Sans | Geist / Inter | Body text, UI |
| Mono | Geist Mono | Code, prices |
| Arabic | Cairo | Darija headlines, CTAs |

## Language Strategy (CRITICAL)

- **Headlines & CTAs**: Tunisian Darija in Arabic script
- **Body text**: French
- **This mix is intentional** — do NOT normalize

```tsx
// ✅ Correct
<h2 className="font-cairo">علاش جاي؟</h2>
<p>Découvrez nos catégories de produits</p>

// ❌ Wrong — don't translate Darija to French
<h2>Pourquoi êtes-vous ici ?</h2>
```

## Component Patterns

- Use shadcn/ui components — never create custom versions
- Modify via `className` prop, never edit `components/ui/` files
- Use `cn()` from `lib/utils.ts` for conditional classes
- Custom classes: `.btn-dodo`, `.badge-promo`, `.card-dodo` (defined in globals.css)

## Empty States

- Use placeholder content for missing images
- Show meaningful messages when no data (e.g., no reviews, no packs)
- Keep consistent dark theme in empty states
